      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const item = $input.first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    subject: item.subject || '',\n    sender: item.from?.value?.[0]?.address || '',\n    body: item.text || item.html || ''\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        -144,
        -48
      ],
      "id": "4f3e96df-029d-45aa-b569-4889619cfd9b",
      "name": "Code in JavaScript"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Subject:{{ $json.subject }}\nBody:{{ $json.body }}\nSender:{{ $json.sender }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are an AI email classifier for a business acquisition automation system.\n\nYour task is to determine whether an email is related to a REAL business acquisition / business-for-sale opportunity.\n\n\n\n## INPUT\n\nSubject: {{ $json.subject }}\nSender:{{ $json.sender }}\nBody: {{ $json.body }}\n\n\n## OUTPUT RULE\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON in the following format:\n\n{\n\"isBusinessAcquisition\": true,\n\"subject\": \"subject\",\n\"sender\": \"sender\",\n\"body\": \"body\"\n}\n\nOR\n\n{\n\"isBusinessAcquisition\": false,\n\"subject\": \"subject\",\n\"sender\": \"sender\",\n\"body\": \"body\"\n}\n\n## CLASSIFICATION RULES\n\nReturn true only if the email is clearly related to:\n\n* Business for sale\n* Company acquisition opportunity\n* Broker sending a deal\n* Owner looking for a buyer\n* M&A opportunity\n* Private company sale listing\n* Acquisition target introductions\n* Business broker outreach containing a specific business opportunity\n\nReturn false for:\n\n* Ads / marketing emails\n* Newsletters\n* Personal emails\n* Ecommerce order emails\n* Job offers\n* Recruitment emails\n* General investment news\n* Vendor outreach\n* Software promotions\n* Cold sales emails\n* Support tickets\n* Funding announcements\n* Startup news\n* Generic investment opportunities without a specific business for sale\n\n## IMPORTANT RULES\n\n* Return ONLY valid JSON\n* Do NOT explain your reasoning\n* Do NOT add markdown\n* Do NOT add code fences\n* Do NOT add any extra fields\n* Preserve the original subject, sender, and body exactly as provided\n* If uncertain, return false\n"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
