      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Analyze this email:\n\nSubject: {{ $json.output.subject }}\nSender:{{ $json.output.sender }}\nbody:{{ $json.output.body }}",
        "messages": {
          "messageValues": [
            {
              "message": "You are a deal analyst for Madison Lane Capital.\n\nExtract ALL information from this email and score the deal.\n\nEXTRACT these fields:\n- company_name: business name from email\n- industry: type of business\n- geography: location mentioned\n- asking_price: any price mentioned (number only)\n- revenue: any revenue figure (number only)\n- ebitda: any EBITDA figure (number only)\n- broker_name: sender name\n- broker_email: sender email\n- description: 2-3 sentence summary\n- red_flags: list of concerns (empty array if none)\n- source: \"Email\"\n\nSCORING (add points for what EXISTS in email):\n- Revenue $500K+           → +2 points\n- EBITDA margin 15%+       → +2 points\n- Asking price < 5x EBITDA → +2 points\n- Location USA             → +1 point\n- Low/no red flags         → +2 points\n- Growth potential visible → +1 point\n\n- fit_score: total points (0-10)\n- fit_reasoning: explain what data was found and why this score\n\nReturn ONLY raw JSON, no markdown, no backticks."
            }
          ]
        },
        "batching": {}
      },
